I have for sale an AR lower I built over the course of the last few months. It has pretty much everything you could want in an AR lower and has never been fired. I have pre filled up those magazines with 90rds total of federal lake city ammo. All in all I have invested about $500 in to this build and hate to part with it, but the wife and I just bought a Jeep that became the new play toy.
